description: Naruto and Minato combine their powers to perform a Sage Jutsu attack on Obito. Obito decides to speed up his plan to perform the Infinite Tsukuyomi and summons the Divine Tree.
title: The Divine Tree

description: The Divine Tree is close to blossoming, and Madara declares that there is only 15 minutes left before everything comes to an end.
title: A Shinobi's Dream

description: The Allied Shinobi Forces begin their onslaught against Obito and Madara. But Ten Tails suddenly transforms and hurls powerful Tailed Beast Bombs toward distant towns.
title: The Ties That Bind

description: The barrier is shattered, and Ten Tails appears! With unfathomable power in its attack, it sends shock waves through the air.
title: The Allied Shinobi Forces Jutsu

description: Shikaku outlines his final strategy, in which Nine Tails will send its chakra to increase everyone's strength. United in their cause, Naruto and the Allied Shinobi set out to take on Ten Tails.

input: Those Who Dance in the Shadows

title: Those Who Dance in the Shadows

description: As the fighting rages on between the Senju and Uchiha, Hashirama approaches Madara about an alliance. But Madara refuses to listen and releases Susano'o instead!
title: Era of Warring States

description: As children in a strife-filled time, Hashirama meets Madara Uchiha and the two talk about their hopes for the future.
title: Hashirama and Madara

description: Ten Tails' relentless attack is wearing down Naruto, and his chakra begins to dissipate. Meanwhile, Kakashi and Obito face each other in a different Kamui dimension.
title: Hole

description: Ten Tails is on the brink of its final transformation and begins to form a massive Tailed Beast Bomb.
title: Something to Fill the Hole

description: Standing on the cliff where they first confided their hopes to each other, Hashirama and Madara gaze at their burgeoning village.
title: My True Dream

description: After listening to what Hashirama and the rest of the former Hokage have to say, Sasuke decides on the path he will ultimately take.
title: Sasuke's Answer

description: Team 7 is finally reunited when Naruto, Sakura and Sasuke join forces. Then the reanimated former Hokage arrive to add their strength to the counteroffensive.
title: Team 7, Assemble!

description: Sakura focuses on her healing skills while Naruto and Sasuke aim for Ten Tails. Meanwhile, the five Kage battling Madara have sustained critical injuries.
title: The New Three-Way Deadlock

description: Kakashi holds on to the hope that Obito can return to being the young man that he remembers. But Obito has abandoned the present as well as the memories of his friends and will not try to stop the Infinite Tsukuyomi.
title: Kakashi vs. Obito

description: Part 1 of a special two-part extra edition! The townspeople are going about their daily business on the streets of the Leaf Village when someone suddenly appears and starts sending them flying!

input: The Directive to Take the Nine-Tails!

title: The Directive to Take the Nine-Tails!

description: Part 2 of a special two-part extra edition!  Lee and company rush over and encounter a strange man who is so strong that even Neji can't defeat him.
title: Naruto vs. Mecha Naruto

description: Obito completely absorbs the giant Ten Tails, undergoes a transformation and becomes the Ten Tails' Jinchuriki.
title: The Ten Tails' Jinchuriki

description: Hashirama and Madara continue their old grudge match and fiercely battle while the other shinobi are unable to do anything but watch helplessly from the sidelines.
title: An Opening

description: Minato is filled with regret during his confrontation with Obito.
title: The Day Naruto Was Born

description: The Allied Forces receive a report that Omoi has deserted his post, much to the Raikage's shock.
title: Run, Omoi!

description: Hashirama, Tobirama, Hiruzen, the Five Kage, Orochimaru and every shinobi on the battlefield join together to cut down the Divine Tree!
title: Pursuing Hope

description: The reanimated shinobi appearing before Gaara and Ohnoki is revealed to be none other than Madara Uchiha himself.
title: Madara Uchiha

description: The power of the reanimated Madara Uchiha far exceeds what the Allied Forces expected. The remaining Kage arrive for support, and for the first time in all of shinobi history, the five Kage are united to face their greatest foe.
title: The Five Kage Assemble

description: Naruto and Killer Bee face off against the masked man originally thought to be Madara Uchiha.

input: The Unbreakable Mask and the Shattered Bubble
Unbreakable Mask and the Shattered Bubble

title: The Unbreakable Mask and the Shattered Bubble

description: Naruto and Killer Bee take on the six Reanimated Jinchuriki, who've been equipped with the Rinnegan.
title: Jinchuriki vs. Jinchuriki!!

description: Kakashi and Guy arrive in the nick of time to back up Naruto and Killer Bee. The fight intensifies even further when three out of the six Reanimated Jinchuriki enter Tailed Beast State.

input: Four Tails, the King of Sage Monkeys
Tails, the King of Sage Monkeys

title: Four Tails, the King of Sage Monkeys

description: As Naruto continues to try and free Four Tails from Madara's control, Nine Tails begins to undergo a surprising change.
title: Kurama

description: The tide of battle is slowly shifting in the Allied Forces' favor, but many are uncertain that they really stand a chance against Madara Uchiha.
title: Promise of Victory

description: Naruto uses up the last of his chakra trying to free the Tailed Beasts from Madara's control.
title: Two-Man Team

description: Sasuke goes after Itachi and learns that his brother intends on stopping Kabuto's Reanimation Jutsu alone.

input: The Risks of the Reanimation Jutsu

title: The Risks of the Reanimation Jutsu

description: Sasuke and Itachi team up to stop Kabuto's Reanimation Jutsu.
title: Sibling Tag Team

description: Itachi declares that Kabuto's actions will not lead to what he truly desires and prepares the Uchiha's Ultimate Visual Jutsu that determines an adversary's fate!
title: The Izanami Activated

description: Thanks to Itachi, the Reanimation Jutsu is released, and all the Reanimated Shinobi are returned to their resting places. But to everyone's surprise, the real Madara still remains!
title: Reanimation Jutsu, Release!

description: The Five Kage watch helplessly as Madara activates his Perfect Susano'o to destroy them.
title: I Will Love You Always

description: In order to learn the truth behind the Leaf's actions, Sasuke decides to resurrect the one man who can help him find the answer—Orochimaru.
title: Orochimaru's Return

description: Kakashi is disturbed to discover a strange connection between the masked man's Transportation Technique and his own Kamui Jutsu.
title: Who Are You?

description: Naruto and the others are further shocked when they learn that Obito has been working with Madara Uchiha for years to orchestrate Project Tsuki no Me.
title: Obito and Madara

description: Obito works to rehabilitate his injured body in the hopes of being reunited with Kakashi and Rin.
title: I'm in Hell
